Hey George,
If you look at what Karl wrote, I think what he's saying is if the 
exhaust valve is open during the misfire, then you get the backfire in 
the exhaust (exploded muffler).  However, if the intake is open during 
the misfire, then you mess up the AFM (but not the exhaust).

Mike
